Package: lingmo-watchdog
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, lingmo-filemanager
Description: Watchdog for Lingmo Desktop
 A daemon that monitors the Lingmo File Manager process
 and automatically restarts it if it crashes. 